Body: Description: Hello team, we've been presenting issues now with SQL_ServerSettings scans that keeps aborting mid execution with no logs, the porcess is still alive and have to kill it manually; same thing that happened with sensitive data scan. Please advise. I am attaching logs and dumps
Next Steps Updated: inspect job logs

What We've Learned Updated: Received procdump and screenshots.
Require customer to provide job logs

Reviewed job logs uploaded by customer- it looks like there are a lot of cyberark password errors. Since customer is on 11.6.90, if they were using Cyberark prior to v11.6.0.86 then they would need to reconfigure as the integration has changed
